> "heritrix --admin=LOGIN:PASSWORD", the computer just prints "heritrix 
> is starting ............" and forever. I waited for 10 minutes but it 
> didn't print the lines it is supposed to print. Any one can help me on 
> this?

process before rerunning Heritrix.
